snippet.title: Apex Legends Gameplay Deep Dive Trailer
snippet.description:
Conquer with character in Apex Legends™, a free-to-play* battle royale game where
legendary challengers fight for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. The next
evolution of battle royale is here.

Play for free on Xbox One, PlayStation 4, and Origin for PC: http://x.ea.com/55915
